{"tid":1993823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家明明港共先係攬炒派，我地係防止攬炒派，但我地認同對家詞彙自認攬炒係咩玩法?","createTime":"2020-04-29T04:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T14:32:27.000Z","uid":31215,"like":20,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0b71c7d8a7e1ccdaddb1d95882f3d04398b63bac","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月港共搞到香港點呢??<br />\n<br />\n<ins>惠譽指港府開支巨降港評級至AA，7個月兩度調低</ins><br />\n惠譽認為，根深柢固的社會政治分歧仍未解決，給香港商業環境帶來揮之不去的不確定，並增加了公眾不滿情緒再度爆發的風險，或會進一步破壞國際社會對香港治理、體制和政治穩定的看法。此外，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港與內地經濟，金融和社會政治聯繫逐步增加，這趨勢更因中央政府自1997年回歸以來對香港事務愈來愈高調發聲而顯而易見，可證兩者各自的主權評級更緊密融合。</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>郭官判詞傳歐美 港仲裁中心夢碎</ins><br />\n<br />\n<ins>印度﹕針對中國投資審查新規 適用香港</ins><br />\n報道引述其中一位官員指出，如何看待香港投資是常識，與來自中國投資並無不同。另外兩名官員指出，不會對來自中國及香港的投資作出區分，並表示會以同樣的方式審查來自兩地資金流入。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>人權組織：美賦予「獨立關稅區」若不保港將陷末日</ins><br />\n<br />\n屌你港共硬推中共融合先係攬炒派<br />\n但佢日日抹黑我地先係攬炒香港<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUozVS5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUozVS5.jpg&h=12a3d48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMYwdEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMYwdEY.jpg&h=49bafed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地仲要認同佢<br />\n自認攬炒<br />\n送個正當性俾佢拉攏中間派係咩玩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由而家起<br />\n攬炒派 = 港共<br />\n攬炒形式係硬推中港融合<br />\n<br />\n我地係防止攬炒派<br />\n35+係爭取力量阻止不合理中港融合，保國際地位<br />\n示威係反對港共繼續打橫黎損國際聲譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛香港，拒攬炒，保國際地位<br />\n香港再出發，重新爭取國際競爭力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596959b4a3fe88ec545f5c89a06cc2a3354abd2c","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24956f7b1640fdcf98eb7bee889cea179a03c36d","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56f3592c587a30a6d49d35d0c6133b5b606d8c7","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fc98a4d0c3225dd900b3fecfe4fb431a6961ac","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205b74090eb42a98dde77aec719335b2da7e651f","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2665c2888bc04412c4ff867c95b29a51a42fbf","tid":1993823,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202